<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.8.4">
<l>cilampumutal kalaṉaṇintōr ceṅkaṇ kuṉṟan tikaḻntateṉat tiruvuruvam paṉṟi yāki,</l>
<l>ilaṅkupuvi maṭantaitaṉai yiṭantu pulki yeyiṟṟiṭaivait taruḷiyavem mīcaṉ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>pulampuciṟai vaṇṭolippap pūkam tokka poḻilkaṭoṟuṅ kuyilkūva mayilka ḷāla</l>
<l>valamputiraip puṉalpuṭaicūḻn taḻakār celvat taṇiyaḻuntūr niṉṟukanta vamarar kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Īśa who was gracious, becoming a boar in divine form,</l>
<l rend="indent">wearing an ankle band and other jewels,</l>
<l rend="indent">like the glittering of a red-eyed mountain,</l>
<l>Scooping up the shining earth lady, embracing [her],</l>
<l rend="indent">and keeping her between his tusks,</l>
<l>Behold, is the king of immortals who is happy</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in lovely, prosperous Aḻuntūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">beautiful, encircled on its sides by waters of shifting waves,</l>
<l>As peacocks dance [and] as coocoos call in every grove</l>
<l rend="indent">where areca trees cluster and where bees with thrumming wings hum.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
